      "message": "nit: To avoid surprises, it\u0027s better to define DEP and DSTDIR as local variables for this function. As in:\n\n    local DEP DSTDIR\n    DSTDIR\u003d$1\n    ...",
      "revId": "eb2a6b186d13f085e16c771d8c1919978b8fc58e",
